snippet.title: Best VGM 1596 - Suikoden III - Cheerful Farm Village (Chisha)
snippet.description:

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation 2
Suikoden III (2002)
Cheerful Farm Village (Chisha)
Michiru Yamane, Keiko Fukami & Masahiko Kimura
